726839f-a.title: Queens: Hawtree Avenue - Rockaway Boulevard
726839f-a.text:
Hawtree Ave. (Hawtree Creek Road), east side, near Rockaway
Boulevard, showing a Vanderveer house, which subsequently became the
property of the Hopkins Estate, who sold to New York City.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
